x-3
\begin{align} x-3=3-x&\text{ and }x-3\ge 0&\quad\text{ or }\quad&&-(x-3)=3-x\text{ and }&x-3<0 \\ x-3-3+x=0&\text{ and }x\ge 3&\quad\text{ or }\quad&& x-3=x-3\text{ and }&x<3 \\ 2x-6=0&\text{ and }x\ge 3&\quad\text{ or }\quad&& x-3-x+3=0\text{ and }&x<3 \\ 2x=6&\text{ and }x\ge 3&\quad\text{ or }\quad&& 0=0\text{ and }&x<3 \\ x=3&\text{ and }x\ge 3&\quad\text{ or }\quad&& \text{(true) and }&x<3 \\ &x=3&\quad\text{ or }\quad&& x<3& \\ &&x\le 3& \end{align}
